snippet.title: It's Coming Home (Teaser)
snippet.description:
20 years of hurt never stopped us dreaming! Wrestling that puts the fun first is coming home to Nintendo in January to kick-start 2021:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/wrestling-empire-switch/

"I know that was then, but it could be again."

If you can forgive the football analogy, there are some poignant parallels to draw from this Euro 96 anthem.

Other wrestling games appear for context. Thanks to the YouTubers too numerous to mention who played them so that I don't have to! None get roasted more than my own at 1:20.
